# 🗂️ CRM Data Model

## Overview

This folder contains the data model used in the **CRM Sales Pipeline Dashboard** developed in Power BI.

The dashboard is built using a relational data model that connects multiple datasets to enable accurate KPI calculations, interactive reporting, and business insights.

---

## 📸 Data Model Preview

![CRM Data Model](crm-data-model.png)

---

## 📊 Tables Included

- **sales_pipeline** – Sales opportunities, deal stages, deal values, and sales dates.
- **accounts** – Customer information, industry, revenue, and employee count.
- **products** – Product details, product series, and sales price.
- **sales_teams** – Sales agents, managers, and regional offices.
- **metadata** – Supporting reference data used in the project.

---

## 🔗 Relationships

The data model follows a relational structure by connecting the datasets using appropriate one-to-many relationships. This enables:

- Accurate KPI calculations
- Efficient DAX measure creation
- Interactive filtering across visuals
- Consistent business reporting

---

## 💼 Skills Demonstrated

- Data Modeling
- Relationship Management
- Power BI Model View
